T1  - Customers' Optimal Joining Rules for the GI/M/s Queue
AU  - Yechiali, Uri
Y1  - 1972/03/01
PY  - 1972
DA  - 1972/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.18.7.434
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.18.7.434
